.TH esmtp_auth 4gx "" "Gromox" "Gromox user reference"
.SH Name
esmtp_auth \(em SMTP authentication proxy
.SH Description
.PP
esmtp_auth is a service plugin for smtp(8gx) which proxies authentication
requests to (yet another) SMTP server. When this plugin is in use, authmgr(4gx)
needs to be disabled.
.SH Configuration file directives
.SS cache_size
.PP
Default: \fI0\fP
.SS retrying_times
.PP
Default: \fI2\fP
.SS scan_interval
.PP
Default: \fI1 minute\fP
.SH See also
.PP
\fBgromox\fP(7)
